data.title: What is Chengdu B Z Score? 600880.SHG
data.meta_description: Chengdu B Z Score is currently at 0.0. Z-Score is a simple linear, multi-factor model that measures the financial health and economic stability of Chengdu. The score is used to predict the probability of a firm going into bankruptcy within next 24 months or two fiscal years from the day stated on the accounting statements used to calculate it. The model uses five fundamental business ratios that are weighted according to algorithm of Professor Edward Altman who developed it in the late 1960s at New York University..
